{
  "id": "6323dbcd4c3dd3001deaad8c",
  "title": "なんでも知っている馬鹿",
  "created": 1663294416,
  "updated": 1692937275,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6323dbcd4c3dd3001deaad8c",
      "text": "なんでも知っている馬鹿",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcee6003500006d8bbd",
      "text": ">「なんにも知らない馬鹿がいるし」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bbe",
      "text": ">山系君が警戒する様な顔をしている。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bbf",
      "text": ">「なんでも知っている馬鹿もいる」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc0",
      "text": ">「いますかね」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc1",
      "text": ">「いる。学は古今に通じ、識は東西にあまねくして、それでどう見ても[馬鹿]なんだ。あんなのは困るね」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1671939299
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc2",
      "text": ">「だれの事ですか」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc3",
      "text": ">「だれがどうと云うのではない。[一般論]だよ。つまり知っていると云うだけで、それだけで[お仕舞]なのさ」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1692937275
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc4",
      "text": ">「はあ」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc6",
      "text": "[内田百閒]の[阿房列車]シリーズのどこかに書いてあるはずだが実物は未見[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc7",
      "text": "　検索すると[新潮文庫]の第三阿房列車に載っているらしいことは分かる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc8",
      "text": "　　[https://jariroji.livedoor.blog/entry/20110303/p6#more]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bc9",
      "text": "　　[https://www.shinchosha.co.jp/book/135635/ 内田百閒 『第三阿房列車』 | 新潮社]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bca",
      "text": "　しかし前述の文が書いてある作品の、百閒センセイが付けた元のタイトルが分からない...",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bcb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bcc",
      "text": "cf. [知識メタボリック症候群]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bcd",
      "text": "　[外山滋比古]の幾つかの著書に出てくる用語のようだ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bce",
      "text": "　例えば[乱談のセレンディピティ]第7章[文殊の知恵]の冒頭など（Googleブックスで確認）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bcf",
      "text": "　　[乱読のセレンディピティ]ではない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "6323dbcfe6003500006d8bd0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1663294416,
      "updated": 1663294416
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7c527e6003500006c9755",
      "text": "cf. [知識と知恵]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1671939367,
      "updated": 1671939370
    },
